{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations","doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio\/init(ratio:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Defines a WCAG 2.1 ratio with the given contrast ratio value"}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio\/init(ratio:)"]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Foundations"}],"externalID":"s:15OUDSFoundations15OUDSWCAG21RatioV5ratioACSd_tcfc","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"init","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"init"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"ratio"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sd","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Double"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"roleHeading":"Initializer","title":"init(ratio:)"},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"init","kind":"keyword"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"ratio","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Double","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sd","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"ratio","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The contrast ratio to use"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/OUDSWCAG21Ratio":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Some countries set up new laws so as to force companies to have a better accessibility of their digital services."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This is for example the case for France with the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"also named “RGAA”."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This utility helps to define wether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"See for example "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"}],"title":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Contains a set of helpers and extensions shared for higher level targets."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations","title":"Foundations","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_layers.png"}],"role":"collection"},"ic_layers.png":{"identifier":"ic_layers.png","alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSFoundations\/ic_layers.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations/OUDSWCAG21Ratio/init(ratio:)":{"identifie